  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4864922">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4864922/" class="title-link">周易古经集注</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4864922"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/43683863/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u43683863-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/43683863/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">会太极的金猪</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-03-19"
      class="main-meta">2011-03-19 13:50:06</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4864922_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  余观此书，乃考据学术研究之用书,非占卜之流尔。  若有求占卜之人，可略过矣。  然专研古籍文献者，此书则可读矣。  从文字中可看出，作者对古文字的来历精熟，且推论有据。 成书年早，宜与周易尚氏学同参，则学术益精进矣。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4864922/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 2没用</span>
